member.summary:
All translated messages for the requested scope
Key: Message key, Value: Translated text
Example: { "Validation.General.Required": "This field is required" }

All messages for the page organized by section
Example: {
  "Validation": { "Required": "This field is required", ... },
  "Labels": { "ProductCode": "Product Code", ... },
  "Buttons": { "Save": "Save", "Cancel": "Cancel", ... }
}
